public class Solution {
  public int closest(int[] array, int target) {
    if (array == null || array.length == 0) {
      return -1;
    }
    int left = 0;
    int right = array.length - 1;
    while (left < right - 1) {
      int mid = left + (right - left)/2;
      if (array[mid] == target) {
        return mid;
      } else if (array[mid] < target) {
        left = mid;
      } else {
        right = mid;
      }
    }
    //post-prcessing
    if (Math.abs(array[left] - target) >= Math.abs(array[right] - target)) {
      return right;
    } else {
      return left;
    }
  }
}

// left 0 4
// right 6 6
// mid 3   5



2. 两个需要记住的小知识点，一是绝对值 Math.abs(),二是判断句 XXXXXX ? yes : no;

Math.abs(array[left] - target) >= Math.abs(array[right] - target) ?  right : left;

3. left < right - 1 这一块注意一下，不要形成死循环，及时跳出loop
